<main>
  <div class="container px-4 py-5">
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-xl-2 align-items-md-center g-5 py-2">
      <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-start gap-2">

        <div class="container border-bottom px-0 py-2 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">  
          <div>
            <h2 class="m-0" id="title-vacancy"><%= @vacancy.code %> - <%= @vacancy.title %></h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm" id="liveToastBtn" onclick="copyText()">Copiar</button>
          </div>      
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted date-pub pb-5">Publicado em <%= l @vacancy.created_at, format: :long %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Descrição da vaga</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.description %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Requisitos</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.requirements %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Habilidades desejadas</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.desired_skills %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Salário</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= number_to_currency @vacancy.salary_range %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Benefícios</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.benefits %></p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold">Jornada de trabalho</h3>
        <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.working_day %></p>  
      </div>

      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 g-4">

        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
          <div
            class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mdt fs-4 rounded-3">
            <svg class="bi" width="1.2em" height="1em">
              <use xlink:href="#tools" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-0">Modelo de Trabalho</h5>
            <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.work_model%></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
          <div
            class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mdt fs-4 rounded-3">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
              <use xlink:href="#geo-fill" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-0">Local de Trabalho</h5>
            <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.vacancy_location%></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
          <div
            class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mdt fs-4 rounded-3">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
              <use xlink:href="#speedometer" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-0">Nível da Vaga</h5>
            <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.vacancy_level %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
          <div
            class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mdt fs-4 rounded-3">
            <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
              <use xlink:href="#cpu-fill" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-0">Área</h5>
            <p class="text-muted"><%= @vacancy.field %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid" style="background:#83BA30">
    <div class="container px-4 py-5 text-light">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-white pb-3">Candidatura</h1>
        <p class="candidature">Para se candidatar, é muito simples. Basta enviar um e-mail para 
          <span>rh@instor.com.br</span>, com o código da vaga, nome da vaga e o currículo anexado.</p> 
        <p class="candidature">Muito em breve retornaremos o contato. <span>Boa sorte!</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%= render "shared/footer" %>